Package: kc
Version: __VERSION__
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: willgcr <hello@willgcr.me>
Depends: libc6, libical3t64 | libical3, libcurl4t64 | libcurl4, libncursesw6
Homepage: https://wrklabs.org/kc
Description: terminal calendar with CalDAV and Google Calendar sync
 kc is a minimal terminal calendar. Manages calendars locally in vdir
 format, with two-way CalDAV sync (iCloud and others), Google Calendar
 via OAuth2, ICS subscriptions, recurring events, and attendee RSVP —
 all rendered in a fast ncurses TUI.
